title: Tertio die Nouembris anno .xxi. Henrici.viii. The act agayns kyllyng of calues
author: England. Sovereign (1509-1547 : Henry VIII)
notes: Also contains an act that reads: The acte lymytyng the pryse of hattys and cappys brought frome beyont the see.
